Prolog Unit Tests
=================


---++ What to do with loaded tests?

	* Keep them around
	* Remove them
	* Flag module as `volatile', so it is not saved.

---++ When to run tests?

	* At :- end_tests
	* On User request
	* After make/0
		* requires hook in make

---++ Reporting

	* Use print_message/2

---++ Volatile modules?

